   <body>
      <context>
         <note>This action can only be performed by an FSR. This will
definitively acknowledge a pending alert via the display without the
need to connect to the service port.</note>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>To view the LCM status, select <uicontrol>Diagnosis</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol>LCM status</uicontrol>.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table>
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">LCM status:Tech. check needed</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To definitively acknowledge the pending alert, press the <uicontrol> ENTER</uicontrol> key on the HMI 5 times within 5 seconds while
the alert is shown under <uicontrol>LCM status</uicontrol> on the
screen. The alert is now definitively acknowledged.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
